   "source": [
    "# AI Suggestions Layer\n",
    "Reads months flagged by shortage detection, gathers full context from every\n",
    "Gold view, and asks Gemini for a structured recommendation per month."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 0,
   "metadata": {
